{
  "name": "imagic",
  "private": true,
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "vite",
    "build": "vite build",
    "preview": "vite preview",
    "proxy": "node proxy-server.js",
    "dev:full": "concurrently \"npm run proxy\" \"npm run dev\"",
    "build:github": "cross-env GITHUB_PAGES_SUBDIRECTORY=true vite build --mode production",
    "build:custom": "vite build --mode production",
    "deploy": "node scripts/deploy.js",
    "deploy:github": "npm run build:github && node scripts/deploy.js",
    "deploy:custom": "npm run build:custom && node scripts/deploy.js"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "cors": "^2.8.5",
    "express": "^4.18.2",
    "form-data": "^4.0.0",
    "http-proxy-middleware": "^2.0.6",
    "lucide-vue-next": "^0.525.0",
    "multer": "^1.4.5-lts.1",
    "node-fetch": "^2.6.7",
    "vant": "^3.4.3",
    "vue": "^3.4.0",
    "vue-router": "^4.2.5"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@vitejs/plugin-vue": "^5.0.0",
    "concurrently": "^7.6.0",
    "cross-env": "^7.0.3",
    "vite": "^5.0.0"
  }
}
